## Suspense Strategy

Wrap every async Server Component in `<Suspense>` with a skeleton fallback.

```typescript
// app/[locale]/(dashboard)/chat/page.tsx
import { Suspense } from "react";
import { ChatHistorySkeleton } from "@/components/skeletons/chat/chat-history.skeleton";
import { ChatHistory } from "./_components/ChatHistory";

export default function ChatPage() {
  return (
    <div className="flex h-full">
      <Suspense fallback={<ChatHistorySkeleton />}>
        <ChatHistory />
      </Suspense>
    </div>
  );
}
```

---

## App Directory Files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `layout.tsx` | Persistent shell |
| `page.tsx` | Route content |
| `loading.tsx` | Auto Suspense boundary |
| `error.tsx` | Catches errors — must be `"use client"` |
| `not-found.tsx` | Shown when `notFound()` is called |
| `global-error.tsx` | Root-level catch |

