## Metadata

Export `metadata` from every page:

```typescript
import type { Metadata } from "next";

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "DevMentor AI — مرشدك الذكي",
  description: "منصة ذكاء اصطناعي لتعليم الـ Frontend للمطورين العرب",
};
```

---

## Images

Always use `next/image` — never `<img>`.

```typescript
import Image from "next/image";

<Image src={user.avatarUrl} alt={user.name} width={40} height={40} className="rounded-full" />
```

---

## Rules Summary

- ✅ Default to Server Components — `"use client"` only when necessary
- ✅ Always `await params` and `searchParams` in Next.js 15
- ✅ AI calls go in `app/api/` Route Handlers — not Server Components
- ✅ Wrap async Server Components in `<Suspense>`
- ✅ Use `next/image` — never `<img>`
- ❌ Never put `"use client"` on pages or layouts
- ❌ Never call AI APIs from the client directly
